Mo Li.

00:06:28.080 --> 00:06:29.440
What do you want?

00:06:31.390 --> 00:06:32.200
Money?

00:06:33.120 --> 00:06:34.150
Company shares?

00:06:35.244 --> 00:06:36.440
I'll give it all to you.

00:06:36.760 --> 00:06:38.150
Whatever you want, you can have it.

00:06:38.760 --> 00:06:39.680
Let Gu Liusu go first.

00:06:39.680 --> 00:06:40.866
Put the knife down, okay?

00:06:40.888 --> 00:06:42.030
